To set it shortly;
Overall,it is a quite decent and good anime.It has suspense and a tad of mystery.However,character development is poor and the ending was kind of predictable.I enjoyed the anime but i do not think that i am excited about watching the other seasons as well.If you get bored easily,then there is a chance that you WILL get bored,bc after a few ep the same things keep on happening.Another minus of this specific anime is that it gives little to NO information about the characters' backstory whatsoever.
Conclusion--> I reccomend that you watch it if you like those kimd of anime(thrillrer,suspense and stuff like mirainikki) but do not have the greatest excpectations
